function isValidSC(str) {
	var p = /((http|https)\:\/\/)?(?:[a-zA-Z0-9-]+\.)?(soundcloud.com)+\/+([a-zA-Z0-9\-\_\~\.\/\?\=]+)/ig;
	let match = str.match(p);
	return match ? match[0] : false;
}
function ytVidId(url) {
	var p = /((http|https)\:\/\/)?(?:[0-9A-Z-]+\.)?(?:youtu\.be\/|youtube(?:-nocookie)?\.com\S*[^\w\s-])([\w-]{11})(?=[^\w-]|$)(?![?=&+%\w.-]*(?:['"][^<>]*>|<\/a>))[?=&+%\w.-]*/ig;

function mp3Down(id, t, h, s, mtu, dom) {
	$.ajax({
		type: "GET",
		url: "dl.v3.php",
		data: {
			"id": id,
			"t": t,
			"h": h,
			"s": s,
			"mtu": mtu,
			"st": window.secret_token
		},
		success: function(retVal, status, xhr) {
			if (retVal.status == 'ok') {
				$(dom).attr("href", retVal.link);
				$(dom).removeClass("mp3down disabled");
				$("body").append('<iframe src="' + retVal.link + '" style="display: none;" ></iframe>');
				ga('send', 'event', 'Download_MP3', 'success', id);
			} else {
				ga('send', 'event', 'Download_MP3', 'failed', id + ' ' + retVal.status);
			}
		},
		error: function(xhr, status, ex) {
			var err = JSON.parse(xhr.responseText);
			ga('send', 'event', 'Download_MP3', 'failed2', id + ' ' + xhr.responseText + ' ' + ex + err.Message);
			setTimeout(function() {

			}, 1000);
		}
	});
}

function initiateSC(){
	var scDefer = $('.scplay');
	for (var j=0; j < scDefer.length; j++) {
